Title: Got Silk?
Description:
Strange noises comin' from over at the Silken Fields.

Strange smells, too.

Almost makes you think that they could use a cash-strapped $c to complete a few odd jobs for 'em. Make a few pieces of gold.

Or not.
ObjectivesText: Report to Silkmaster Tsai at the Silken Fields in Valley of the Four Winds.
RewardText: Greetings, $c. Welcome to the Silken Fields.
